        "question_html": "<p><span class=\"english\">ছকের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বামপাশে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">প্রদত্ত</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বাগ্‌ধারার</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সাথে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ডানপাশে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">প্রদত্ত</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">অর্থের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">মিলকরণ</span><span class=\"english\"> কর</span><span class=\"english\">।</span><span><span> </span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span> </span></span><span class=\"english\"><span> </span>৫</span></p><p><span><img src=\"images/Varsity_Kha_Weekly_Live_Exam-05_Set_3_a68c7290.png\"/></span></p>",
